      • getUploadData

        public UploadData getUploadData()
        Returns UploadData instance that provides access to upload data. Changes will not be applied until the setUploadData(UploadData) method is called.
        返回提供对上传数据的访问的UploadData实例。在调用setUploadData（UploadData）方法之前，不会应用更改。
        Returns:
        UploadData instance that provides access to upload data or null if request doesn't contain data for upload. 提供对上传数据的访问权限的实例，或者如果请求不包含要上传的数据的实例。

      • setUploadData

        public void setUploadData(UploadData uploadData)
        Modifies upload data for the current HTTP request. The given uploadData will be sent to a web server as part of HTTP request.
        修改当前HTTP请求的上传数据。给定的uploadData将作为HTTP请求的一部分发送到Web服务器。
        Parameters:
        uploadData - the upload data that will be sent to a web server. -将要发送到Web服务器的上传数据。
